                    email,
                    fullName,
                    role,
                    isActive,
                    pageable
            ));
        } else {
            UserResponse currentUser = userService.getUserByEmail(authentication.getName());
            return ResponseEntity.ok(userService.searchUsers(
                    search,
                    currentUser.getId(),
                    email,
                    fullName,
                    role,
                    isActive,
                    pageable
            ));
        }
        
    }

